"6 cups freshly grated sharp Cheddar cheese (1 1/2 lb.)","1/2  (8-oz.) package cream cheese, softened","3/4 cup mayonnaise","1 tablespoon grated yellow onion","1 teaspoon ground red pepper","1  (7-oz.) jar whole peeled pimiento, drained and cut into fourths","  Garnish: freshly ground pepper"